-- Sarkozy Accepts French Government's Resignation; Cabinet Shuffle to Follow
-- B y   D i c k   S c h u m a c h e r
-- 2010-11-13T19:08:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-13/sarkozy-accepts-french-government-s-resignation-cabinet-shuffle-to-follow.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy
today accepted the resignation of Prime Minister Francois
Fillon’s government, setting the stage for cabinet reshuffle
that political analysts have anticipated.  Sarkozy’s office announced the government resignation in an
e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
